OL,3,CNine grieving families call for public
OL,4,Cinquiry into Sussex maternity services
OL,6,FRobyn Davis's son Orlando was starved
OL,7,Fof oxygen at birth and died two weeks
OL,8,Flater. Katie Fowler's daughter Abigail
OL,9,Fwas again starved of oxygen, and died
OL,10,Fafter two days.
OL,12,FMaternity services where Esme and
OL,13,FOrlando were born in Worthing are
OL,14,Fcurrently rated as 'requires
OL,15,Fimprovement'.
OL,17,FThe Royal Sussex County Hospital in
OL,18,FBrighton where Abigail was born was
OL,19,Fmost recently rated by the CQC as
OL,20,F'inadequate'.
