OL,3,CNine grieving families call for public
OL,4,Cinquiry into Sussex maternity services
OL,6,FKatie Fowler said: "I went from being
OL,7,Fthe happiest I'd ever been, I loved
OL,8,Fbeing pregnant, to the absolute
OL,9,Fdevastation of losing my daughter
OL,10,Fcompletely unexpectedly.
OL,12,F"And what has surprised me is I feel
OL,13,Fthat the Trust have managed to somehow
OL,14,Fmake what is already a horrendous
OL,15,Fsituation worse.
OL,17,F"And it's really distressing to know
OL,18,Fthat there were so many other families
OL,19,Fin similar situations."
