OL,3,CNine grieving families call for public
OL,4,Cinquiry into Sussex maternity services
OL,6,FRobyn Davis added: "This keeps
OL,7,Fhappening and therefore we do believe
OL,8,Fthat it is more of a systemic issue.
OL,10,F"We just want the whole care evaluated
OL,11,Fand the learning outcomes to be put
OL,12,Finto place to make sure that this does
OL,13,Fnot happen to any other family,
OL,14,Fbecause we're quite literally all
OL,15,Fliving through hell.
OL,17,F"A public inquiry into maternity
OL,18,Fservices is definitely needed to
OL,19,Freview all hospitals because sadly
OL,20,Fthis is happening everywhere."
