OL,3,CNine grieving families call for public
OL,4,Cinquiry into Sussex maternity services
OL,6,FDr Maggie Davies, chief nurse at
OL,7,FUniversity Hospitals Sussex NHS
OL,8,FFoundation Trust, said: "We offer our
OL,9,Fdeepest condolences and sincere
OL,10,Fapologies to each of the bereaved
OL,11,Ffamilies for their devastating loss.
OL,13,F"Whilst we recognise that no words can
OL,14,Fease their pain, our dedicated teams
OL,15,Fare committed to listening, learning
OL,16,Fand improving the service, so that
OL,17,Fmothers-to-be, mothers and their
OL,18,Fbabies are as safe as they possibly
OL,19,Fcan be whilst in our care.
