OL,3,CNine grieving families call for public
OL,4,Cinquiry into Sussex maternity services
OL,6,F"We have recruited more midwives,
OL,7,Fchanged how we listen to and support
OL,8,Ffamilies, and we have a nationally
OL,9,Frecommended triage process to help
OL,10,Freact quickly if there are any reasons
OL,11,Ffor concern.
OL,13,F"Our outcomes for mothers and babies
OL,14,Fare now better than most other Trusts
OL,15,Fin the country, but we know we must
OL,16,Fcontinue to listen and improve, and
OL,17,Fwould always want to meet any families
OL,18,Fwho have concerns to understand their
OL,19,Fexperiences and make changes where
OL,20,Fpossible."
